INSERT INTO sessions (id, user_id, github_id, github_username, github_access_token, emails, selected_email, created_at, last_activity, expires_at)
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, NOW(), NOW(), $8)
            ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET
                last_activity = NOW(),
                expires_at = $8
